trans-unit.source: Provides constants for compatibility with the Visual Basic 6.0 <xref uid="langword_csharp_ZOrder" name="ZOrder" href=""></xref> method.
trans-unit.target: 提供與 Visual Basic 6.0 的相容性常數<xref uid="langword_csharp_ZOrder" name="ZOrder" href=""></xref>方法。

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], the Visual Basic `ZOrder` method is replaced by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.BringToFront%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.SendToBack%2A> functions.
These constants enable code that has been upgraded from Visual Basic 6.0 to continue to run without additional modification.
trans-unit.target: 這些常數可啟用從 Visual Basic 6.0，才能繼續執行而不需額外修改已升級的程式碼。

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Functions and objects in the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6> namespace are provided for use by the tools for upgrading from Visual Basic 6.0 to [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > 函式和物件中的<xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6>命名空間所提供的工具，以便從 Visual Basic 6.0 來升級[!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]。</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6>

trans-unit.source: In most cases, these functions and objects duplicate functionality that you can find in other namespaces in the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 在大部分情況下，這些函式和物件會複製您可以在其他命名空間中找到的功能[!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)]。

trans-unit.source: They are necessary only when the Visual Basic 6.0 code model differs significantly from the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] implementation.
trans-unit.target: 會需要這些只有當 Visual Basic 6.0 程式碼模型與大幅[!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)]實作。

trans-unit.source: Equivalent to the Visual Basic 6.0 constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbBringToFront" name="vbBringToFront" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 相當於 Visual Basic 6.0 常數<xref uid="langword_csharp_vbBringToFront" name="vbBringToFront" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Equivalent to the Visual Basic 6.0 constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbSend ToBack" name="vbSend ToBack" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 相當於 Visual Basic 6.0 常數<xref uid="langword_csharp_vbSend ToBack" name="vbSend ToBack" href=""> </xref>。
